# Electron IPC surface

- Renderer uses `window.electronAPI` from `src/preload.js` → `ipcMain.handle` in `src/main.js`.
- Renaming or changing an IPC handler requires updating **all three**: `src/main.js`, `src/preload.js`, and every call site in `src/renderer/app.js` (and other renderer modules if applicable).
- Prefer extracting logic with stable interfaces over rewriting large flows in `src/main.js` or `src/renderer/app.js`.
